{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"海君","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay9yEwn444nOd7MqiaZUa2azD5hTd5tMdu8G8YhwUhtTeAIdquibGaicQc44pkxoSFYYCN4iaEkeecOd4/0","content":"天天看着别人打球，天天看视频篮球技巧，而你却不上场打篮球岂不是白看了白学了吗？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":1131,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487572945000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Mervin","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay298nTPcqnf9qUj2fGrKBWiaM3ggN7ibNSsv79rWylBSdqtAWAOGGDx77ANDhMYGfksL2xNZ4Uc3QW/0","content":"学到的知识，应该内化成能力，才能够为你所用。\n\n就好比开车，考驾照之前你肯定看过非常多的驾驶知识，从汽车如何发动，到各个场景下如何操作，再到交通规则和路灯指示牌等。科目一拿满分的人，起码知识学习得非常的好，但是还是挡不住她们会在科目二、科目三挂掉。甚至很多新手上路，违反交通规则或者出现交通事故，都是因为只知道知识，但是在实际场景下，缺没有办法将知识变为熟练的能力，应用自如。\n\n学习知识是第一步，内化成能力是让知识变得有价值更重要的一步，内化的过程，就是通过实践，把知识操练一边，获得实践中经验，这就是培养「手感」的过程，手感好，才是真得学会了知识，为你所用了。","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":802,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487315352000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"ringa","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjNo0cs2XXHr6wTiaRPFXA6dnc9sRb3icgRaCbnvgqogyGMlp2AR5TDc7RSWqjER3yElaibB2KoIaNF5/0","content":"淀粉如何转化成能量?\n\n首先，要消化\n其次，要消耗\n\n知识首先要自己理解消化，其次输出消耗","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":748,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487167205000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"黄朝高","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6bUYFqibauOEicfQddUdFx7Nabg4HGe5IeOpO0NPUw6f2icIUfljnE3q5lkRu2dtJHfyhB7WlriapqKqMibVpJ3VUu6M/0","content":"这其实就跟卖油翁倒油进铜钱，而钱不湿的道理一样，“唯手熟尔”。所谓实践出真知嘛，学到知识不加以应用，怎么可能内化成能力呢？\n\n\n附文：陈康肃公尧咨善射，当世无双 ，公亦以此自矜。尝射于家圃，有卖油翁释担而立，睨之，久而不去。见其发矢十中八九，但微颔之。\n康肃问曰：”汝亦知射乎？吾射不亦精乎？”翁曰：”无他， 但手熟尔。”康肃忿然曰：”尔安敢轻吾射！”翁曰：”以我酌油知之。”乃取一葫芦置于地，以钱覆其口，徐以杓酌油沥之，自钱孔入，而钱不湿。因曰：”我亦无他，唯手熟尔。”康肃笑而遣之。\n此与庄生所谓解牛斫轮者何异？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":728,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1487087949000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"程然","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/TVwhicV1539IW2Fx75h6RibeXpgwkiaTloWbvWZibHU3ulLlIhhE6iaIiazJaXkXaYkTTbdwvhdOM7cvxOoQpCxud7DYns8icjZDZ7w/0","content":"人是如何消化食物的  \n首先是摄入的选择，是依据自己的喜欢暴饮暴食？还是均衡营养，平衡膳食？可以类比我们对知识的摄入，是随心猎奇？还是加以限制，跳出舒适区？\n其次是消化。食物的消化是分步骤的，从口腔咀嚼的初步处理到胃储存的细致处理，从小肠对营养物质的吸收到大肠对废物的处理。可以类比知识的内化过程，从刚接触的浅显了解到日积月累的深入探求——学习的持续性，对有益观点的吸收和错误观点的摒弃——学习的批判性。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":674,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486963473000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"东科","submitUpdateTime":"2017-02-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/bsgZwYlfZ5uFsmGzOPSz6YnGQ6ZicuSurUvzmhalbiaQiakdH7AcC5Hoxoa4M0tvXWr4QruqiaIJtqbvWMnIPgWtTSwc8hqvcqibN/0","content":"类比“沙漠中是如何淘金的”\n（1）选择一片有含金量的沙漠。选择有内容的知识；\n（2）运用科学的方法对沙子进行筛选，比如密度不同的方式进行淘沙。把获得的知识按照自己的知识框架进行获取\n（3）按照提取物的不同，将提出出来的金子归类整理；按照运用场景不同把知识进行归类；\n（4）想要获得更多的金子，需要大量的沙子重复进行提取；要想把知识变成能力需要进行大量的练习；\n（5）金子要成为有价值或者变现，需要到市场中进行交易，否则只是金色的石头；而懂得的知识要变成能力，需要运用到自己的工作和生活当中，才能变成能力，否则只是知识。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":589,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1486689466000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Evelyn","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FfnPYQicNKvU8piclQWvZStXH9QBFyxhlvc0JG22elM8ickAaGywcjhbN8GfGA1icDZvLMuglIsEHTrt/0","content":"占坑，待回答","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":310,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484826542000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Lynn","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaS788fT3wfr0z1OvK2SUQrQBPFCibx11kKuZYLthgg6icGycO74jXczau1fM9XffsiaicBDjeQbJq1yEz/0","content":"如何把一堆砖头变成一座漂亮的房子？\n\n各种各样的知识就如同一块块砖头，你需要挑选合适的砖头，然后用辅助材料把它们堆积成不同的形状，最终盖成一座房子。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":303,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484824271000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"藤蔓","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoMia9Hm7ZPz616AibGDibl1nqZ0VjhkZ4ybnKCNglesZnNvicAouzwpDFVJ9abOflBtJcr7LicJ6FJcHr/0","content":"放着回来答","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":243,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484738961000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"柚子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKQ9yoT3nbNKdxAfx36YXu2S1KS39tFaY2Biaj1Ax9EC2EFm7YL9S2bhnYO900iaLz2YBl7tPsiaN5msXdt9Z7ibzrD/0","content":"类比“食物该如何转化为能量”\n（1）要选择有利于增加能量的食物类别，即要选择能促进想提升的能力选择知识；\n（2）就像食物需要咀嚼一样，知识也要细化成知识点；\n（3）食物要经过消化，知识也要经过掌握\n（4）食物消化后原来的形态结构都发生了变化，转化为糖，知识掌握后也不再单纯是知识本身，而是与自身结合，转化为自己的“知识”\n（5）糖要消耗、用起来才能提供能量，已经转为为自己的知识也要在用的过程中转化为能力","voteCount":1,"commentCount":1,"submitId":86,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1484559031000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"对方正在讲话…","submitUpdateTime":"2017-01-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoCvboE3blaO28YFp4fluZAiaWt3pUUKWUbGMemym4ntgFsxZDdiaugdqkcnnVubxV2I0yHc0zF7iatV/0","content":"把知识内化为能力，我首先想到的点是实践，唯有实践经验足够，才能真\n   正的化为己用。正所谓“纸上得来终觉浅，绝知此事要躬行“实践一定是把知识内化为\n   能力